graph.author: FGI
graph.description: Version 0.1; A model to represent activities and information related to the review and evaluation of proposed developments or alterations to a structure.  This model supposes that an official of a government agency must review proposed construction activities and determine whether the activities require conditions/mitigations to conform with local requirements.  This model allows for formal application review and informal (e.g.: pre-application) consultations.
graph.name: Consultation
